arStrings.szText: Breathless, you can't believe what you just saw. You almost died in a particularly cruel way if the player hadn't stepped in.
I told you, this "old man" is trying to deceive you!
You...you were telling the truth. We have been here before! But, how am I...
Emphasis on "have". You finally realize your friend has been telling the truth. You're still dumbfounded how close you came to a grisly death.
(laughs) Very clever! Very cunning! I yield. Come then, if you are not afraid!
Iâ€”Of course I am not afraid! I will make you show yourself!
Trying to suddenly throw on a mask of false bravado. The "I" should feel like you are as unsure as previous lines before you catch yourself and puff your chest up.
